1
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,320
[Under the Moonlight]

2
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:29,700
[Adapted from the novel
"Jin Nang" by Shui He]

3
00:01:31,220 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 25]

4
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:35,360
The steward of the Qin family
didn't want me.

5
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:37,120
He thought I was too young.

6
00:01:37,950 --> 00:01:39,000
No matter how Qin Yi pleaded,

7
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,910
it was useless.

8
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,360
Just then, Wuniang passed by

9
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:44,230
and took a liking to me at first sight.

10
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,680
She made the decision

11
00:01:46,270 --> 00:01:47,870
to bring me back to her place.

12
00:01:49,230 --> 00:01:51,360
At that time, I was a maid,

13
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:53,120
but I didn't have to do any rough work.

14
00:01:53,910 --> 00:01:55,480
Every day, I just followed her

15
00:01:55,720 --> 00:01:57,800
to learn the rules, needlework,

16
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,760
and music and arts.

17
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:02,480
Wuniang was a kind-hearted person.

18
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:03,720
She treated you

19
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,800
like her own daughter.

20
00:02:05,190 --> 00:02:06,680
At first, I felt that way too.

21
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,110
I was very grateful.

22
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,800
But later, I realized

23
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,320
she was raising me

24
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,800
like a tool,

25
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,960
something to be refined.

26
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:19,910
Something that one day

27
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,910
could bring her favor

28
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,000
and make her money.

29
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,600
You all want to see me

30
00:02:25,830 --> 00:02:27,600
make a fool of myself, right?

31
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:30,390
Want to see me thrown out,

32
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,720
leaving in tears?

33
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:35,670
Not a chance!

34
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,030
I have no interest

35
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:39,080
in the Qin family.

36
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,630
When I get to Mingke House,

37
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:42,800
I will naturally live

38
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,630
a life of luxury.

39
00:02:44,830 --> 00:02:47,030
I'll eat well and live lavishly,

40
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,320
far better

41
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:50,910
than in your shabby place.

42
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,550
Let's go.

43
00:02:55,670 --> 00:02:57,160
Wuniang, I don't want to go.

44
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,110
Please let me stay.

45
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,080
I raised you,

46
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,630
so you're mine.

47
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,630
Wherever I go,

48
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,800
you must follow.

49
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,670
Got it?

50
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:06,520
Let's go.

51
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:09,470
Wuniang,
I don't want to go to the music house.

52
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:16,000
You ungrateful wretch!

53
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:18,160
I raised you with so much difficulty,

54
00:03:18,830 --> 00:03:20,520
and you dare to despise me?

55
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,030
Get up and go.

56
00:03:23,550 --> 00:03:24,160
Let's go.

57
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,110
Madam,

58
00:03:30,110 --> 00:03:32,320
please let me stay, Madam.

59
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,190
I was bought by the Qin family.

60
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:36,750
You can't let me go, Madam.

61
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,320
It's getting late.

62
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,630
Let's send Wuniang on her way.

63
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:44,910
Sanniang!

64
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:47,240
Siniang!

65
00:03:52,390 --> 00:03:54,630
There's not a decent person
in the Qin family.

66
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,240
Get out of here!

67
00:04:16,350 --> 00:04:18,110
Ruyi,

68
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:19,640
help me.

69
00:04:19,790 --> 00:04:21,550
I don't want to go, Ruyi.

70
00:04:21,790 --> 00:04:23,670
Please help me talk to Mr. Qin.

71
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:58,070
Wuniang, you should leave quickly.

72
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,230
Take your dirty things with you

73
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,640
and get out of here!

74
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,830
You wretched boy,

75
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:20,670
I should have killed you back then.

76
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,510
I shouldn't have let you live.

77
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:27,880
Go!

78
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,880
During my years with the Qin family,

79
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,390
I always regarded Qin Yi

80
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,880
like my own brother.

81
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,230
I thought he was the only person

82
00:05:49,230 --> 00:05:50,920
I could rely on in this world.

83
00:05:51,110 --> 00:05:52,040
Ruyi,

84
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,480
look what this is.

85
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:55,950
What is this?

86
00:05:56,110 --> 00:05:57,640
A sweet melon, very sweet.

87
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,550
Here, try it.

88
00:05:58,670 --> 00:05:59,480
Sweet melon?

89
00:06:02,790 --> 00:06:03,600
Is it sweet?

90
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:06,950
So sweet!

91
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,510
Where did you get it?

92
00:06:08,670 --> 00:06:09,950
A merchant from beyond the pass

93
00:06:09,950 --> 00:06:11,440
gave it to Wuniang.

94
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:12,600
Wuniang?

95
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:14,920
So sweet!

96
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:18,510
You shameless woman!

97
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,760
You shameless woman!

98
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:20,950
How dare you interfere

99
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:22,670
in my business from beyond the pass?

100
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,480
I didn't do anything.

101
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,950
I'm being wronged.

102
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:27,480
I've always been loyal to you!

103
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,070
Still defiant?

104
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:28,640
I...

105
00:06:28,640 --> 00:06:29,880
You're so defiant!

106
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,390
So defiant!

107
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:30,950
How could I possibly...?

108
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,950
How dare you.

109
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:32,830
Please stop, Mr. Qin.

110
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:33,640
How dare you.

111
00:06:33,790 --> 00:06:35,160
Mr. Qin, please stop!

112
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,600
Mr. Qin!

113
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:40,000
It wasn't until I went to Mingke House

114
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,000
that I gradually realized

115
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:43,920
he had been using

116
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,200
my trust in him

117
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,950
to ruthlessly bring down Wuniang.

118
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,040
It was from that day

119
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:52,670
that I finally understood

120
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:58,070
that I can only rely on myself.

121
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,830
People like him

122
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:02,000
are not worth befriending.

123
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:04,040
Just stay away from him.

124
00:07:22,110 --> 00:07:23,110
Ruyi.

125
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,950
Yulan!

126
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:31,670
Long time no see.

127
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:34,110
Why don't you

128
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:36,320
call me brother?

129
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:39,320
I'm an orphan. I have no brothers.

130
00:07:39,830 --> 00:07:40,920
You always called me

131
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,000
brother before.

132
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:43,110
Yulan,

133
00:07:43,790 --> 00:07:44,510
from now on,

134
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,950
you don't have to be afraid anymore.

135
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:46,880
Now,

136
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:48,950
I am the master of the Qin family.

137
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:52,070
Congratulations, Mr. Qin.

138
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:54,790
I came specifically to take you home.

139
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,760
Come with me.

140
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,880
I know you've always resented me,

141
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:07,230
but you should understand

142
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:09,320
that I wanted to help you back then.

143
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,950
It was just that
I didn't have the ability.

144
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,830
At that time, I was insignificant,

145
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:16,920
and one misstep

146
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,350
could have angered my father,

147
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,790
bringing disaster upon myself.

148
00:08:20,070 --> 00:08:21,440
So I told myself

149
00:08:23,110 --> 00:08:25,200
that enduring for a moment
can lead to great achievements.

150
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,000
Yulan,

151
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:29,600
could you please

152
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,950
give me another chance?

153
00:08:32,710 --> 00:08:33,710
I want to make up for these two years...

154
00:08:33,710 --> 00:08:34,550
Mr. Qin,

155
00:08:35,910 --> 00:08:37,230
you owe me nothing.

156
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,910
I don't need you
to make up for anything.

157
00:08:43,030 --> 00:08:44,910
I'm no longer called Yulan.

158
00:08:45,350 --> 00:08:46,000
Just as

159
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,470
you are no longer Ruyi.

160
00:08:53,470 --> 00:08:54,440
It's all in the past.

161
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,440
You are no longer Yulan,

162
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,230
nor are you Jin Nang.

163
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,280
You are now Luo Shu,

164
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,200
the one I admire most.

165
00:09:06,030 --> 00:09:06,840
Rest assured,

166
00:09:07,590 --> 00:09:08,590
from now on,

167
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,280
everything will get better.

168
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:22,590
Mrs. Guo.

169
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:27,080
Luo, you're here!

170
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,400
I want to ask you

171
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,550
about what happened back then.

172
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,230
Darling, come out!

173
00:09:33,230 --> 00:09:34,320
Look who's here!

174
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:41,280
Stop! Who are you?

175
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,640
What are you doing?

176
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:45,150
This is Mr. Menglin.

177
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:46,590
How dare you stop him?

178
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,670
Mr. Menglin, what brings you here?

179
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,400
I came to ask you something.

180
00:09:52,350 --> 00:09:53,150
Please come in.

181
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,080
What do you want to ask?

182
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:05,000
You've been in the army for a long time.

183
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,280
I want to ask you

184
00:10:06,350 --> 00:10:07,150
who was in charge of military supplies

185
00:10:07,470 --> 00:10:08,840
thirteen years ago.

186
00:10:10,230 --> 00:10:11,550
What kind of supplies?

187
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:12,880
Petroleum.

188
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:15,790
I can't remember that.

189
00:10:16,470 --> 00:10:17,550
There must be a roster.

190
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:21,230
Even if there is a roster,

191
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:22,760
it wouldn't be for me to see.

192
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,760
Who has the roster?

193
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:25,840
Take me to see him.

194
00:10:26,350 --> 00:10:27,000
Mr. Menglin,

195
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,910
please don't
make things difficult for me.

196
00:10:29,150 --> 00:10:29,960
Breaking the rules

197
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,840
can lead to military punishment.

198
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,670
How about this?

199
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:36,880
You can go and ask at home first.

200
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:39,080
If the governor gives you a pass,

201
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:41,000
you can investigate whoever

202
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,710
or whatever you want.

203
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:50,960
Take care, Mr. Menglin.

204
00:10:55,110 --> 00:10:56,150
Help yourself.

205
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:58,400
Mr. Guo,

206
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,400
thirteen years ago,

207
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:02,670
a few days after my house was burned,

208
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,280
there were several people
at the alley entrance

209
00:11:04,280 --> 00:11:05,710
asking about the fire at my house.

210
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,960
Do you remember?

211
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:10,200
How could I forget?

212
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,910
The day after your house caught fire,

213
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,910
two strangers

214
00:11:15,110 --> 00:11:17,400
were wandering near the ruins.

215
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,000
When they saw me,

216
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:20,320
they asked me

217
00:11:20,350 --> 00:11:22,150
about the fire.

218
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:25,440
They even asked if anyone survived.

219
00:11:25,710 --> 00:11:26,840
I thought those two

220
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:28,760
looked suspicious,

221
00:11:29,350 --> 00:11:30,760
so I didn't tell them the truth.

222
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,710
Do you remember what they looked like?

223
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:33,790
Any distinguishing features?

224
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:37,790
What did they look like?

225
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:42,320
It was too long ago.

226
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,670
I can't remember clearly.

227
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:47,710
The food is getting cold.

228
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:50,790
Luo, have a bun.

229
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:51,470
Yes.

230
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:54,880
Mr. and Mrs. Guo, take your time eating.

231
00:11:55,110 --> 00:11:56,200
I'll leave now.

232
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,080
You should eat before you go.

233
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:58,910
No, thanks.

234
00:11:59,350 --> 00:12:00,200
I'll eat the bun

235
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,790
on the way.

236
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,640
Girl, eat before you leave.

237
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,440
Luo,

238
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,230
What is it, Mr. Guo?

239
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,200
I still...

240
00:12:12,030 --> 00:12:12,840
I...

241
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:17,670
I remember something.

242
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:21,440
But if I say it,

243
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:24,200
I'm afraid
it'll tarnish your father's reputation.

244
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,440
What is it?

245
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,710
I remember

246
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:28,640
the day your house caught fire.

247
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:33,790
Hello.

248
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:35,710
Guo.

249
00:12:35,710 --> 00:12:36,440
Qingfeng.

250
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,590
What's going on?

251
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:41,030
You've bought so many nice things.

252
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:42,230
You know what, Guo,

253
00:12:42,230 --> 00:12:43,760
I won today!

254
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:45,350
You won?

255
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,760
A fellow worker

256
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:47,520
invited me

257
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:49,320
to play a few rounds
at Changsheng Gambling House.

258
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:50,440
Unexpectedly,

259
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,110
it was my first time gambling,

260
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:53,230
and I ended up winning

261
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:54,110
against all those veterans.

262
00:12:55,470 --> 00:12:56,350
That's great!

263
00:12:56,350 --> 00:12:57,760
You should take me next time.

264
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,520
I want to try my luck too.

265
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:00,440
Sure.

266
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:03,280
I just bought chicken and fish today.

267
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:04,280
Come over for a drink.

268
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:06,200
I can't.
I still have deliveries to make.

269
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,440
Alright, let's do it another day.

270
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,590
Another day.

271
00:13:08,590 --> 00:13:09,280
Take care.

272
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,350
Alright.

273
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:15,150
Changsheng Gambling House?

274
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:16,880
Is it still around?

275
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:19,000
Yes, over to the east.

276
00:13:19,350 --> 00:13:20,590
Just two streets away

277
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:22,080
from our Dongjiaxiang.

278
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:29,520
Don't worry, I didn't say anything.

279
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:40,320
This is a sin.

280
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:43,470
What a good girl Luo is,

281
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:45,910
and we're deceiving her.

282
00:13:47,110 --> 00:13:49,110
Put away your compassionate heart.

283
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:51,350
Our son is in their hands.

284
00:13:51,710 --> 00:13:52,960
How can we refuse to do

285
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,080
as they say?

286
00:13:55,470 --> 00:13:57,080
They have money and power.

287
00:13:57,880 --> 00:14:00,470
Can ordinary people like us
afford to offend them?

288
00:14:01,110 --> 00:14:01,880
But

289
00:14:01,880 --> 00:14:03,760
we watched Luo grow up.

290
00:14:04,350 --> 00:14:06,760
She's just like our own daughter.

291
00:14:07,280 --> 00:14:09,280
