434
00:19:31,800 --> 00:19:32,920
I need your help.

435
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:33,950
Go ahead.

436
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,470
Who went
to the Changsheng Gambling House

437
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:36,760
