00:24:28,760 --> 00:24:29,830
Alright, fine!

527
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:31,350
I'll talk, alright?

528
00:24:31,710 --> 00:24:32,710
You scoundrel!

529
00:24:34,350 --> 00:24:35,400
Thirteen years ago,

530
00:24:36,040 --> 00:24:36,800
that minor official

531
00:24:36,800 --> 00:24:37,710
from the granary of Taiyuanwei

532
00:24:37,710 --> 00:24:38,880
